islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:26:04.000Z","msg":"有冇歐洲線窮撚攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:36:55.000Z","msg":"KLM走寄艙行李"},{"pid":"c1f75dee6c4cb019d6bc277a6ef85c05b667f699","tid":1761254,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfbf90caece6b6d8f81175ff30d09417878515e9","tid":1761254,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:26:04.000Z","msg":"有冇歐洲線窮撚攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\nAirline方面我個人prefer長+短航程，長個程可以直接瞓耐啲。同埋通常長＋短嘅公司落機係朝早，可以用盡啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（所以我唔係咁中意中東三寶，瞓得三四粒鐘就要起身轉機。）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想平同埋CP值高可以留意以下呢幾間：VN SK QR SQ BR EY<br />\n(唔推薦EK 一來EK偏貴 二來A380真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> AY出少左優惠 CX 9-10月有超早鳥直航歐洲)<br />\n歐洲carrier多航點不過service差啲。通常呢幾個航點會平啲: <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAMS MAD BCN ARN MXP CPH CDG<br />\n機型有得選盡量 B777 &gt; A350 &gt; A330 (= A340) &gt; B787 &gt; ...&gt; 奴隸船。<br />\n除非你有被虐傾向同埋好中意人多，又或者好想試A380，如果唔係可免則免。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nA380打手咪當人水魚啦 垃圾當上菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n[長篇]「追尋自由之路」波羅的海+芬蘭11日 [2018]<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/KbKtOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/KbKtOU</a>"},{"pid":"3f3fcc4432aed7b13c06a88e74f47f0c88b13999","tid":1761254,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7757ea5f5093998e8e28fb7d12cc759ec330a488","tid":1761254,"uid":195998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c9ec8ee1576eda6615c61f295f7034f474f8c93","tid":1761254,"uid":57827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote