"tid":1761254,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://booking.etihad.com/SSW2010/EYEY/webqtrip.html?execution=e4s1&amp;cid=undefined\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooking.etihad.com%2FSSW2010%2FEYEY%2Fwebqtrip.html%3Fexecution%3De4s1%26cid%3Dundefined&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=0b2c7c99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://booking.etihad.com/SSW2010/EYEY/webqtrip.html?execution=e4s1&amp;cid=undefined</a><br />\n<br />\n樓豬 Etihad 4070 兩程787<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a60fc364afa8ecc157811d34ea6879676ff838","tid":1761254,"uid":105121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"216fb9962cc8896abdd4f6676ba8aa4e884c04a3","tid":1761254,"uid":77165,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"615baf53ffc2d9e950d72169256b120ce9f745be","tid":1761254,"uid":203471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:47:21.000Z","msg":"二月尾想飛轉MXP<br />\n上網睇吓發現各大Airline都同價<br />\n想睇下邊間坐得舒服D<br />\n1) CX: B777 - $4600 (Direct flight)<br />\n2) QR: B777 A350 - $4100 (未坐過)<br />\n3) ER: A380 x 2 - $4200 (成日坐)<br />\n4) SQ: B777 A350 - $4600 (未坐過)<br />\n5) BA: A380 A319 - $3300 (感恩節大減價？)<br />\n個人而言 始終坐成十幾粒鐘 想坐得舒服D 又想坐下新機型 <br />\n想各位巴打指點迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:52:01.000Z","msg":"如果ba a380劃到上層窗口二人位係唔錯 又靜<br />\n不過啲機都有啲年紀 上次坐個IFE全行壞晒 升晒上PEY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:46:17.000Z","msg":"唔止d機啦 d人都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd0c790d366601ba0b9e70e8703f11001e94504","tid":1761254,"uid":203471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"如果終極對決 a350 vs b787🤔<br />\nPS. EY回程係早機 MXP 9點幾出發 蝕左成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5d50f966f39d2833a846f4ac3282ad94111076","tid":1761254,"uid":14449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:23:51.000Z","msg":"Qatar<br />\n轉機行下個機場都幾好"},{"pid":"936787961a546710e42bf7c68622a2d3c9361e12","tid":1761254,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"上次係heathrow 返香港<br />\n坐qatar a380機<br />\n去check in行李好似中國春運咁<br />\n個個勁撚多行李<br />\n等勁耐先搞掂<br />\n上機又係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89753c960a94512045beb4e59fc701eb1374cb5a","tid":1761254,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"我揀BA<br />\n<br />\n雖然BA服務係閪d,但長+短落機冇咁辛苦而且平d<br />\n話說呢幾日AF有sale都可以睇下"},{"pid":"e2f0da7bcb0ef890fddc56e926df18cf26af8257","tid":1761254,"uid":88420,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"dfbf90caece6b6d8f81175ff30d09417878515e9","tid":1761254,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:26:04.000Z","msg":"有冇歐洲線窮撚攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T12:55:16.000Z","msg":"撇除送中果幾間大陸航空<br />\n要最平一定係 Air France - KLM 集團跳樓價<br />\n$3500 以下就入手啦<br />\n雖然法航 777 難民船真係坐得好辛苦<br />\n但係酒水好好 只要你當坐長途巴士咁就會接受到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者等漢莎集團（漢莎 &amp; 瑞士）or 英航定期減價<br />\n呢幾間公司成日打價格戰 長途機票越來愈平<br />\n漢莎如果搭到 A340 或者 A380 係唔錯的<br />\n服務水平非常穩定 無驚喜但係唔會失望<br />\n試過來回香港 可以一覺訓天光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再唔係就芬蘭航空 / SAS<br />\n不過佢哋嘅 discount 好似比較難捉摸<br />\n而且部分酒水或者小食係要俾錢的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個人對中東三寶非常有保留<br />\n首先佢哋價錢已經唔係最平<br />\n幾年前漢莎法航未減價 仲收緊七八千嘅時候<br />\n經中東當然係抵<br />\n但係依家佢哋 service 又開始 cut（Etihad <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n中東去歐洲個程，你側邊班旅客嘅質素又唔知係點<br />\n同埋飛行時間實在太差 訓訓下覺就要起身轉機<br />\n<br />\n最後，因航緊係唔搭啦，賣港求榮，你睇下佢近年嘅服務同 777 奴隸船，就知道佢放棄曬香港 O&amp;D 班客。無眼睇。"},{"pid":"1515307bd80c5345a2d6ac2674bbfc4129839056","tid":1761254,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"Econ間間都差唔多<br />\n一係就CX直航<br />\n一係就BA慳翻d錢<br />\n<br />\n差嗰幾舊水連埋轉機坐多8個鐘真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad9ad86bc8589d9665b7616611d92d3713518fd","tid":1761254,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bbd93db5b04d62fe6da23e466d7869389827b94","tid":1761254,"uid":224453,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"615baf53ffc2d9e950d72169256b120ce9f745be","tid":1761254,"uid":203471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:47:21.000Z","msg":"二月尾想飛轉MXP<br />\n上網睇吓發現各大Airline都同價<br />\n想睇下邊間坐得舒服D<br />\n1) CX: B777 - $4600 (Direct flight)<br />\n2) QR: B777 A350 - $4100 (未坐過)<br />\n3) ER: A380 x 2 - $4200 (成日坐)<br />\n4) SQ: B777 A350 - $4600 (未坐過)<br />\n5) BA: A380 A319 - $3300 (感恩節大減價？)<br />\n個人而言 始終坐成十幾粒鐘 想坐得舒服D 又想坐下新機型 <br />\n想各位巴打指點迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:50:26.000Z","msg":"A380啦 唔坐就冇機會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:13:55.000Z","msg":"揀女都係A380<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdf0b1e83a70c3c143184c85e053d3d10e9251c","tid":1761254,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:18:56.000Z","msg":"qr啦,cx奶共不了"},{"pid":"78aeccbb06b7dc1bc0b88b592d0c02458a6bdccd","tid":1761254,"uid":224453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ad9ad86bc8589d9665b7616611d92d3713518fd","tid":1761254,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bbd93db5b04d62fe6da23e466d7869389827b94","tid":1761254,"uid":224453,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6